{"tid":1021074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【當更警１分】機場報案中心　警員涉私吞市民拾獲銀包被捕","createTime":"2019-02-14T04:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T11:38:14.000Z","uid":6497,"like":147,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4f7fdeab1843656cfdce0611ad1c9227717f3b","tid":1021074,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190214/large/1550116068_09cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190214%2Flarge%2F1550116068_09cb.jpg&h=95f60337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場客運大樓報案中心，懷疑有警員監守自盜，私吞市民拾獲的銀包。拾遺者聯絡物主後揭發事件，警方拘捕一名涉案警員調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，昨晚11時左右，有市民在機場內撿獲一個銀包，內有5萬港元，於是好心交到客運大樓的報案中心；由於銀包內有物主的聯絡電話，該名市民也同時致電物主，告知銀包已交予警方。<br />\n約3小時後，物主到報案中心報失及認領，這才揭發事件並沒立案，懷疑有人監守自盜；警方經調查後拘捕一名涉事警員。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》正就事件向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方程序，負責處理這類失物案的警員，須將拾遺者的資料用電腦記錄，並向對方發出收據；之後將拾獲財物移交財物室，當物主領回失物時亦需簽署收據。"},{"pid":"c1d6a0e888ee0cb14ab10421c795bc2579412a97","tid":1021074,"uid":77196,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"5萬蚊，隻狗係咪咁撚窮呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde2edc0e6b6caad504fd8161f879e1a85685d84","tid":1021074,"uid":37757,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"最大犯罪集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b59bc6a7d101b3085573abcd36eb18933adf562","tid":1021074,"uid":35014,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a97578d3dbced1834813de7ecd0a306a0b47ed4","tid":1021074,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc5a2d8846b48195e3e738638d2a14a80f9d851","tid":1021074,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"